title: Game Pack 3 - Casino Games (Fake Money)
description:
Casino Slotz 1.3.1
Try your luck at slot machines in this 3D environment. Casino Slots has Random Number Generators (RNG) which are continually generating so the game play is always changing. This is a nice way to try out your luck on slot machines without using real money. 

Blackjack 1.6.5
LastEnd Blackjack features an online high scoreboard that allow you to compare your skills against other players from around the world. So come see if your the best by downloading our free Blackjack video game software using the download button located on this page.

Basic Rules
 The player draws cards to an initial two card hand with the object of bringing the total hand value as close as possible to 21 without exceeding it
